reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are Incredible
reviews.reviewText: I have done a lot of traveling but for some reason never got into the packing cubes. On my recent trip to Greece I decided to finally get them and try them out and I am so glad I did. These are perfect for keeping all of your clothes organized and so you can pack more. It was so nice to just grab the cube for the item I needed instead of rummaging around in my suitcase looking for it. On this trip we did a lot of moving around to different hotels and it was so easy to pack up my suitcase and go with these. I will definitely be using these for all my future travels.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 15, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great to get organized!
reviews.reviewText: Oh my goodness these are so helpful. They helped me organize and STAY organized for a trip. They all fit perfectly into any suitcase and make packing so much easier. There were even enough cubes for me to put a pair of shoes in (which is 100% a plus). The only thing that would concern me is the durability. The zippers seem a bit cheap and I’m worried that they might come off. Other than that, great purchase overall!
